description: More than 500,000 queen scallops are moved to allow an internet cable to be laid off the Isle of Man.
title: More than 500,000 queen scallops moved for internet cable
title_page: More than 500,000 queen scallops moved for internet cable - BBC News
maintext: More than 500,000 queen scallops have been caught and rehomed off the Isle of Man coast to allow an underwater cable to be installed, the government said.
